title: 082 - Freight Cakes, Ice Rats, and Bad National Anthems
description:
This week, Levi explores the potential of Cold Stone Steve Austin. Caleb is unsure if a pepper is a fruit. Freight's fame pulls people away from Bob's table. And Tim is in a Gospel trans.
